Text.Page:
Lets see...giant demons...giant eyes...yep, this one's right up your alley.

You're after the {@LinkCreature:9#1400#Azarel's juggernauts} and {@LinkCreature:9#1410#labyrinthine stalkers}.

Bring their eyes...don't give me that look, I just dish 'em out...bring their eyes to Noleta.
When the gulas see their precious monsters with their eyes ripped out, maybe they'll "see" that we aren't kidding around out here, eh?

The labyrinth is a dangerous place, but you look like you can handle it.

You CAN handle it, right?
